data.name: Volcanic Counter
data.desc: When you take battle damage while this card is in your Graveyard: Banish it from your Graveyard, then if there is a FIRE monster other than "Volcanic Counter" in your Graveyard, inflict damage to your opponent equal to the amount of battle damage you took.

card_sets.set_name: Onslaught of the Fire Kings Structure Deck
